dismissalComment.html: a massive wicket for New Zealand! quicker ball, very full, goes straight through Sarwan who looks to come down to it, plays all over it and is cleaned up, he trudges off, and do the West Indies' chances trudge off with him?  there are still a couple of able hitters left to come in and partner Jacobs, no slouch himself, but without Sarwan it is a big ask
